Project goals and features

- Full CRUD, Routing and Error handling with Express
- Use of MongoDB through Mongoose (and interaction between multiple schemas)
- Usage of middlewares for express
- Usage of passport (local startegy only) for Auth
- Understanding the real life use of asyinc/await in JS
- Add server side validation for DB Objects with Joi 
- Use of Cookies and Session to manage users login + understanding the use and possibilities
- Practice with Bootstrap
- Use of Flash to display messages
